OL,3,CTeenagers 'lucky' to be rescued after
OL,4,Cattempting to camp during Storm Dave
OL,6,FA Cumbrian mountain rescue team says a
OL,7,Fgroup of teenagers were 'lucky' to be
OL,8,Frescued after being called out in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of Storm Dave.
OL,11,FPatterdale Mountain Rescue Team were
OL,12,Fcalled out shortly after 9pm yesterday
OL,13,F(4 April) after receiving reports that
OL,14,Fa group of teenagers needed assistance
OL,15,Fat Priest Hole.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
