OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775495152
OL,3,CTeenagers 'lucky' to be rescued after
OL,4,Cattempting to camp during Storm Dave
OL,6,FThe group had been intending to
OL,7,Fwildcamp, but failed to reach Priest
OL,8,FHole and were 'fearing for their
OL,9,Flives' as Storm Dave battered the
OL,10,Fregion and conditions 'were at their
OL,11,Fworst.'
OL,13,FA full call out was initiated after it
OL,14,Fwas said that the teenagers had no
OL,15,Ftent protection and were cold and wet.
OL,16,FDue to the location of the incident
OL,17,FPenrith Mountain Rescue Team were also
OL,18,Frequested.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
