CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775495152
OL,3,CTeenagers 'lucky' to be rescued after
OL,4,Cattempting to camp during Storm Dave
OL,6,FOn arrival the rescue teams found one
OL,7,Fperson suffering mild hypothermia. The
OL,8,Fgroup were treated on scene, given
OL,9,Fmedication and warmed up before
OL,10,Fwalking back down the hill.
OL,12,FFollowing the six hour operation, the
OL,13,Fmountain rescue teams are urging
OL,14,Fpeople to check the weather forecasts
OL,15,Fand avoid exposed locations during
OL,16,Fstorms, as looking for 'stricken wild
OL,17,Fcampers, puts everyone's lives in
OL,18,Fdanger unnecessarily.'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
