OL,3,CTeenagers 'lucky' to be rescued after
OL,4,Cattempting to camp during Storm Dave
OL,6,FPatterdale Mountain Rescue also say
OL,7,Fthat Priest Hole can be hard to find
OL,8,Fin the dark especially in wild
OL,9,Fconditions.
OL,11,FThere were 23 volunteers involved from
OL,12,FPatterdale and Penrith Mountain Rescue
OL,13,FTeams.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
